name: BPOD_HEN_026
description:
beautiful piece of darkness #026 on HEN



I try to turn not so beautiful things, at least visually, into something beautiful. It's about making it obvious, but at the same time I want to hide it. There are limits for words, but not for the imaginary. I like to create things that have a strong expression, but I don't like to describe them. What have I created it for if I still have to explain it? I will continue until I find what I am looking for. What am I looking for? What we are all looking for…

🖤✨
